《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》指出，这种空椅子上摆放诺贝尔奖证书，象征着西方联合行动督促中国大陆政府走向更开放和更民主的未來，而演员乌曼用英文念出刘晓波的文章是向北京领导人挑战，該報又稱那些杯葛頒獎禮的國家是「北京寵物」（{{lang|en|The pet [[北京狗|Pekinese]]}}）<ref>{{cite news|title="China uses muscle to reinforce Nobel ban"|newspaper=《泰晤士報》|date=2010-12-08|author=David Charter|author2=Jane Macartney}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=阿桑奇進監牢 中國抵制諾貝爾|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/uk/2010/12/101208_press_review_daily.shtml|publisher=BBC 中文网|accessdate=2011-01-10|date=2010-12-08|quote=《泰晤士報》稱18個參與抵制諾貝爾和平獎的國家是「北京寵物」。|archive-date=2010-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101211103852/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/uk/2010/12/101208_press_review_daily.shtml|dead-url=no}}（該句須查看網頁的-{zh-hans:源代码; zh-hant:原始碼}-才能見到。）</ref>。

《[[独立报|独立报]]》周六社论标题：「空座椅的雄辩」，将刘晓波和1975年获得和平奖的[[安德烈·德米特里耶維奇·薩哈羅夫|安德烈·薩哈羅夫]]比较，当时的[[苏联|苏联]]政府也对西方干涉苏联内政怒不可遏。「虽然苏联不让关押在牢中的萨哈罗夫领奖，但准許他的妻子可代為領獎；相反地，中国大陆政府不让任何与刘晓波有关系的人前往奥斯陆。萨哈罗夫获奖的16年后，[[蘇聯解體|苏联便解体]]，也许中国共产党的政府也会遭到同样命运。」

《[[卫报|卫报]]》社论：「如果让抵制中國忽視人權的国家把刘晓波印在钞票和邮票上，[[中国人|中国人]]就会想知道他是谁。中国大陆政府会抗拒世界的呼声，还是拒收外国货币呢？<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/go/wsy/pub/email/ft/-/zhongwen/simp/multimedia/2010/12/101211_britain_press.shtml |title=英媒体：诺奖仪式是不同寻常的政治剧作 |accessdate=2010-12-13 |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822061201/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/multimedia/2010/12/101211_britain_press.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>」

===澳大利亚===
颁奖当天，国营的[[澳大利亚广播公司|澳大利亚广播公司]]的电视“[[ABC_24小时|ABC 24小时]]”（ABC News 24）进行了现场直播。《[[澳大利亚人报|澳大利亚人报]]》（The Australian）发表文章《诺贝尔和平奖颁发，呼吁释放刘晓波》。《[[悉尼晨锋报|悉尼晨锋报]]》文章：《诺贝尔主席嘲讽中国的信誉缺憾》。墨尔本的《[[年代报|年代报]]》（The Age）标题：《诺贝尔仪式将荣誉授予缺席的刘晓波》。澳大利亚广播公司一个专题节目中，播放了兩年多前对刘晓波的采访<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/multimedia/2010/12/101211_australia_press_nobel.shtml |title=澳洲各媒体普遍报道诺奖颁奖仪式 |accessdate=2010-12-13 |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822061201/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/multimedia/2010/12/101211_australia_press_nobel.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==中国与挪威的外交关系==
{{main|中挪關係}}
中國在诺贝尔奖后立即中止了两国正在进行的渔业合作谈判及各领域交流活动，政治领域的会面被全部取消<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8055730/China-cancels-Norwegian-fisheries-meeting-in-response-to-Liu-Xiaobo-Nobel-Prize.html|title=China cancels Norwegian fisheries meeting in response to Liu Xiaobo Nobel Prize|last=|first=|date=2010-10-11|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=2016-05-29|archive-date=2016-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807222033/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8055730/China-cancels-Norwegian-fisheries-meeting-in-response-to-Liu-Xiaobo-Nobel-Prize.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":7">{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-nobel-peace-china-idUKTRE6971XY20101012|title=China steps up retaliation against Norway for Nobel|last=|first=|date=2010-10-12|work=Reuters|accessdate=2016-05-29|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629164124/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-nobel-peace-china-idUKTRE6971XY20101012|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

中方还收紧了对进口挪威[[三文鱼|三文鱼]]的限制，甚至一度全面禁止从挪威进口三文魚<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/norway-china-salmon-idUSO9N0QJ00I20140908|title=China bans Norwegian whole salmon imports|last=|first=|date=2014-09-08|work=Reuters|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629161537/http://www.reuters.com/article/norway-china-salmon-idUSO9N0QJ00I20140908|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/norways-salmon-rot-as-china-takes-revenge-for-dissidents-nobel-prize-2366167.html|title=Norway's salmon rot as China takes revenge for dissident's Nobel Prize|last=Lewis|first=Mark|date=2011-10-06|work=Independent|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424221946/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/norways-salmon-rot-as-china-takes-revenge-for-dissidents-nobel-prize-2366167.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年时，中国进口三文鱼中92%来自挪威，到2013年时这一比例已大幅降至29%<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ftchinese.com/story/001052014|title=挪威对华三文鱼出口大幅下降|last=|first=|date=2013-08-16|work=FT中文网|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530194012/http://www.ftchinese.com/story/001052014|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同时中国也提高了对挪威其他产品的贸易限制<ref name=":0">{{cite news|url=http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140509/c09norway/|title=挪威政府顾忌中国拒见达赖喇嘛|publisher=纽约时报中文网|accessdate=2015-07-09|author1=RICK GLADSTONE|archive-date=2015-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150728033756/http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140509/c09norway/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年，挪威前首相[[謝爾·馬格納·邦德維克|謝爾·馬格納·邦德維克]]计划到中国参加国际会议遭到拒签，其他众多挪威公民在申请中国签证时也频频被拒<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.norwaypost.no/index.php/news/latest-news/27048-former-prime-minister-denied-visa-to-china-27048|title=Former Prime Minister denied visa to China|work=The Norway Post|date=2012-06-12|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127125126/http://www.norwaypost.no/index.php/news/latest-news/27048-former-prime-minister-denied-visa-to-china-27048|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.voanews.com/content/chinese-still-angry-with-norway-about-nobel-price/1208175.html|title=Chinese Still Angry With Norway About Nobel Prize|work=VOA|date=2012-06-13|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129165114/http://www.voanews.com/content/chinese-still-angry-with-norway-about-nobel-price/1208175.html|archive-date=2016-01-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2012年1月，挪威外交部门高层消息称挪威政府将阻止中国加入[[北极理事会|北极理事会]]，以作为对中国一系列行为的反制措施<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/norway/9038782/Norway-wants-to-block-China-from-Arctic-Council.html|title=Norway 'wants to block China from Arctic Council'|work=The Telegraph|date=2012-01-25|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308205553/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/norway/9038782/Norway-wants-to-block-China-from-Arctic-Council.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2012/jan/25/norway-china-arctic-council|title=Norway could shut China out of Arctic Council after diplomatic snubs|work=The Guardian|date=2012-01-25|accessdate=2016-01-21|first=Jonathan|last=Watts|archive-date=2016-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160126231626/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2012/jan/25/norway-china-arctic-council|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.economist.com/node/21547832|title=Cold shoulder - Norway considers avenging Chinese bullying|last=|first=|date=2012-02-08|work=The Economist|accessdate=2016-05-29|archive-date=2016-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160427032310/http://www.economist.com/node/21547832|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但之后挪威政府又表示支持中国成为该组织观察员国<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese_news/2012/02/120214_norway_china_ac.shtml|title=挪威支持中國成為北極委員會觀察員|work=BBC中文网|date=2012-02-14|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2016-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160207093154/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese_news/2012/02/120214_norway_china_ac.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中方外交部对此回应称，两国关系能否改善的关键取决于挪威，继续要求挪威采取“切实措施”恢复两国关系<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2013/01-22/4511358.shtml|title=外交部：中国和挪威关系能否改善关键取决于挪方|last=|first=|date=2013-01-22|work=中国新闻网|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630095257/http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2013/01-22/4511358.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年12月，北京市政府出台新政，对部分国家公民提供72小時過境免簽證游览北京的待遇，其中包括大部分欧洲国家，但{{link-en|挪威國籍法|Norwegian nationality law|挪威公民}}被排除在这一名单之外。有报道称这一国家名单是由[[中华人民共和国外交部|中国外交部]]拟定<ref name=":6">{{Cite news|url=http://www.ftchinese.com/story/001047917|title=中国新签证政策“惩罚”挪威|last=|first=|date=2012-12-07|work=FT中文网|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415045458/http://www.ftchinese.com/story/001047917|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="taken">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2015/03/150304_china_norway|title=中國稱撤職諾獎委員會主席不會解凍中挪關係|date=2015-03-04|publisher=BBC中文網|accessdate=2015-07-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709111147/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2015/03/150304_china_norway|archivedate=2015-07-09|author1=嵇偉 (編)|author2=尚清 (編)}}</ref>。

2013年，挪威{{Le|2013年挪威议会选举|Norwegian parliamentary election, 2013|政府换届}}，新首相[[埃尔娜·索尔伯格|埃尔娜·索尔伯格]]任命与中国关系密切的{{Le|博尔格·布伦德|Børge Brende}}为外交大臣，被视为缓解两国关系之举<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.tnp.no/norway/politics/4033-brende-is-to-be-new-foreign-minister-of-norway|title=Brende is to Be New Foreign Minister of Norway|last=|first=|date=2013-10-14|work=The Nordic Page|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602162248/http://www.tnp.no/norway/politics/4033-brende-is-to-be-new-foreign-minister-of-norway|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.newsinenglish.no/2013/10/17/new-minister-may-melt-china-freeze/|title=New minister may melt China freeze|last=|first=|date=2013-10-17|work=Norway's News in English|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701011343/http://www.newsinenglish.no/2013/10/17/new-minister-may-melt-china-freeze/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中方则仍然称“中挪关系未走出困境”，并坚称两国关系恶化“责任不在中方”<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.163.com/13/1019/10/9BHRNU7700014AED.html|title=外交部回应挪威政府换届：中挪关系未走出困境|last=|first=|date=2013-10-13|work=网易新闻|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624211306/http://news.163.com/13/1019/10/9BHRNU7700014AED.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。期间有报道指出，挪威驻华大使[[司文|司文]]任期已满，但挪威外交部担心中方会拒绝接受新大使的任命，因此一直未任命新任驻华大使<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.aftenposten.no/verden/Norge-tor-ikke-bytte-Kina-ambassador-na-106702b.html|title=Norge tør ikke bytte Kina-ambassadør nå|accessdate=2016-05-28|author=|date=|publisher=Aftenposten|language=no|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701201939/http://www.aftenposten.no/verden/Norge-tor-ikke-bytte-Kina-ambassador-na-106702b.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年，[[達賴喇嘛|達賴喇嘛]]以個人身份訪問挪威，但該國的首相和外交大臣均沒有與他會面<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{cite news|author1=蕭爾 (編)|title=圖丹桑珠抨擊挪威政府拒見達賴喇嘛|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/05/140503_china_tibet_dalailama_norway|accessdate=2015-07-09|agency=BBC中文網|date=2014-05-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709130725/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/05/140503_china_tibet_dalailama_norway|archivedate=2015-07-09|deadurl=no}}</ref>，中方对此表示了赞赏<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-norway-idUSBREA3R0L320140428|title=China approves of Norwegian leaders not meeting Dalai Lama|last=|first=|date=2014-04-28|work=Reuters|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629161534/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-norway-idUSBREA3R0L320140428|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这一行为被挪威民众指责为“懦弱”<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.newsinenglish.no/2014/04/23/coward-politicians-avoid-dalai-lama/|title='Coward' politicians avoid Dalai Lama|last=|first=|date=2014-04-23|work=Norway's News in English|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701004330/http://www.newsinenglish.no/2014/04/23/coward-politicians-avoid-dalai-lama/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年，挪威[[警察保安局|警察保安局]]在年度国家安全评估报告中将中国与俄罗斯并列为“威胁”，指责中国“在挪威境內非法收集情報”<ref name=":4">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/02/150206_norway_china_spy|title=「中國情報活動對挪威構成威脅」|last=|first=|date=2015-02-06|work=BBC中文网|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2015-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151218205846/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/02/150206_norway_china_spy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.tnp.no/norway/politics/4875-norway-intelligence-chief-china-and-russia-spying-on-norway-putin-jinping|title=Norway Intelligence Chief: China and Russia Spying on Norway|last=|first=|date=2015-03-17|work=The Nordic Page|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412221003/http://www.tnp.no/norway/politics/4875-norway-intelligence-chief-china-and-russia-spying-on-norway-putin-jinping|dead-url=no}}</ref>。挪威情报部门也谴责中国政府，称中方对挪威公司进行大规模网络黑客攻击，并有证据指明这些攻击受到中国政府的支持，意图窃取敏感数据和军事机密。这也是首次有[[北约|北约]]国家明确指责中国政府与网络攻击有关<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=http://thediplomat.com/2016/01/towards-the-thaw-seeking-clarity-in-sino-norwegian-relations/|title=Towards the Thaw: Seeking Clarity in China-Norway Relations|accessdate=2016-05-28|author=|date=2016-01-16|publisher=The Diplomat|archive-date=2016-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160327214923/http://thediplomat.com/2016/01/towards-the-thaw-seeking-clarity-in-sino-norwegian-relations/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/cyber-espionage-norways-intelligence-chief-accuses-china-stealing-military-secrets-1546879|title=Cyber-espionage: Norway's intelligence chief accuses China of stealing military secrets|last=Murdock|first=Jason|date=2016-03-01|work=International Business Times|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529103646/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/cyber-espionage-norways-intelligence-chief-accuses-china-stealing-military-secrets-1546879|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cankaoxiaoxi.com/world/20160229/1087331.shtml|title=英媒：挪威首次明确指责“中国黑客”窃取军事机密|last=|first=|date=2016-02-29|work=参考消息|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611015849/http://www.cankaoxiaoxi.com/world/20160229/1087331.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。挪威当局还以危害[[国家安全|国家安全]]為由，驱逐一名在當地[[留学|留学]]的中國[[博士生|博士生]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://cn.nytimes.com/china/20150208/c08norway/|title=挪威以国家安全为由驱逐中国留学生|date=2015-02-08|publisher=纽约时报|accessdate=2015-07-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150325144739/http://cn.nytimes.com/china/20150208/c08norway/|archivedate=2015-03-25|author1=BREE FENG}}</ref>。中国则回应称间谍活动的指控“毫无根据”，“充满[[冷战|冷战]]色彩”；<ref name=":4" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2015-02/5610058.html|title=挪指责“中俄间谍威胁” 中方：指控充满冷战色彩|last=|first=|date=2015-02-06|work=环球时报|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807044557/http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2015-02/5610058.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>还称驱逐留学生的行为“侵犯了中国留学生的基本权益”，并提出交涉<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2015-02-06/122731490676.shtml|title=挪威校方回应中国学者遭驱逐:警方决定毫无道理|last=|first=|date=2015-02-06|work=新浪新闻|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701171215/http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2015-02-06/122731490676.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-norway-idUSKBN0L805A20150204|title=China rebukes Norway for expelling scholar|last=|first=|date=2015-02-04|work=Reuters|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629163104/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-norway-idUSKBN0L805A20150204|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后，[[奥斯陆|奥斯陆]]地方法院裁定驱逐判决无效<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-09/22/c_128254394.htm|title=挪威法院裁定还中国学者清白|last=|first=|date=2015-09-22|work=新华网|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805174711/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-09/22/c_128254394.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在两国关系恶化期间，挪威試圖改善其與中華人民共和國的關係。前[[挪威首相|挪威首相]]、工党的[[延斯·斯托爾滕貝格|延斯·斯托爾滕貝格]]據說曾考慮向中華人民共和國道歉，但他後來改變主意；同屬工党的[[托爾比約恩·亞格蘭|托爾比約恩·亞格蘭]]的諾貝爾委員會主席一職在2015年被撤銷，但中華人民共和國認為此舉對兩國關係不會有影響<ref name="taken" />。

2015年，两国在经济合作方面曾出现关系缓和的征兆。3月，中方以挪威产三文鱼可能含有[[三文魚貧血症|传染性鲑鱼贫血症]]为由，全面禁止进口挪威部分地区产三文鱼<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://no.mofcom.gov.cn/article/jmxw/201503/20150300919512.shtml|title=中国停止进口挪部分地区三文鱼|last=|first=|date=2015-03-23|work=中华人民共和国驻挪威王国大使馆经济商务参赞处|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-05-28|archive-url=https://archive.is/20160528143924/http://no.mofcom.gov.cn/article/jmxw/201503/20150300919512.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/norway-salmon-idUSL6N0WK4HB20150318|title=China imposes new limits on Norwegian salmon imports|last=|first=|date=2015-03-18|work=Reuters|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629161359/http://www.reuters.com/article/norway-salmon-idUSL6N0WK4HB20150318|dead-url=no}}</ref>；但4月时，挪威渔业大臣{{Le|伊丽莎白·亚斯帕克|Elisabeth Aspaker}}称两国已达成协议，中国将接受挪威的检疫标准，同意继续进口其三文鱼产品<ref name=":3">{{Cite news|url=http://www.newsinenglish.no/2015/04/20/china-signals-a-crack-in-the-ice/|title=China signals a crack in the ice|last=|first=|date=2015-04-20|work=Norway's News in English|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160504034117/http://www.newsinenglish.no/2015/04/20/china-signals-a-crack-in-the-ice/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，中国主导的[[亚洲基础设施投资银行|亚洲基础设施投资银行]]接受挪威成为其创始成员国之一<ref name=":3" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/business-32128357|title=Taiwan and Norway sign up to AIIB|last=|first=|date=2015-03-31|work=BBC|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310062839/http://www.bbc.com/news/business-32128357|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://politics.people.com.cn/n/2015/0414/c1001-26844516.html|title=埃及、挪威、俄罗斯正式成为亚投行意向创始成员国|last=|first=|date=2015-04-14|work=人民网|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2015-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150713182706/http://politics.people.com.cn/n/2015/0414/c1001-26844516.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。挪威驻华大使司文在接受中国媒体采访时也表示两国在环保、能源、北极事务等领域的合作仍在继续<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20150402/43473093_0.shtml|title=挪威大使：为改善对华关系，我们在作各种努力|accessdate=2016-05-28|author=|date=2015-04-02|publisher=凤凰网|archive-date=2016-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520193440/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20150402/43473093_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但在政治外交领域，两国关系一直未有解冻迹象<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.newsinenglish.no/2016/02/19/chinese-maintain-diplomatic-freeze/|title=Chinese maintain diplomatic freeze|last=|first=|date=2016-02-19|work=Norway's News in English|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2016-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160224042549/http://www.newsinenglish.no/2016/02/19/chinese-maintain-diplomatic-freeze/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年初，[[台海两岸关系|台海两岸关系]]遭遇一系列风波不断发酵，台湾媒体[[三立新闻台|三立新闻台]]报道称有台灣留學生收到挪威移民局回信，明确表示“挪威認為台灣是一個國家”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=119820 |title=北歐與台友好！抗議簽證誤植中國 挪威承認台灣是國家 |work=三立新闻台 |date=2016-01-20 |accessdate=2016-01-21 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eh3s0rGz?url=http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=119820 |archivedate=2016-01-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，引发中国大陆很多民众的不满。随后挪威外交部媒体负责人回应称挪威“坚持[[一个中国|一个中国]]的立场”“不会改变”，将与移民局沟通此事。挪威驻上海总领事馆和驻华大使馆也先后发表微博表明立场<ref>{{cite web|url=http://taiwan.huanqiu.com/article/2016-01/8418649.html|title=台媒抹黑挪威 挪威外交部否认“承认台湾是国家”|work=环球网|date=2016-01-21|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2016-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160122095135/http://taiwan.huanqiu.com/article/2016-01/8418649.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2016-01-20/doc-ifxnuvxe8255703.shtml|title=台媒称挪威承认台湾是“国家” 挪外交部否认|work=新浪网|date=2016-01-20|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2016-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160122090811/http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2016-01-20/doc-ifxnuvxe8255703.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

